            <title>[HBASE-3567] InterruptedException still swallowed at many places</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3567</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There was &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2791&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;this Bug-Report (HBASE-2791)&lt;/a&gt;, which was dismissed as &apos;redone in the master rewrite&apos;. But for the InterruptedException nothing has changed.&lt;br/&gt;
InterruptedException is swallowed or wrapped in other Exceptions at many places, which is just not right. Please read &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/java/library/j-jtp05236.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;this&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
